## How to Use

1. **Storybook is running at** http://localhost:6006/

- Each component preserves the exact HTML structure from your original template
- All components include Outlook VML fallbacks for buttons
- Mobile-responsive classes (`mobilepadd`, `fluid-image`, etc.) are preserved
- Components can be customized via Storybook controls and the HTML updates automatically
- Users can copy individual component HTML or the complete email template
